## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not fully capture the diversity of experiences and outcomes associated with student entrepreneurship. Additionally, the impact of cultural and economic differences on the feasibility and success of student businesses was not extensively covered. Further research could explore these aspects in more detail.

